com.google.gwt.visualization.client
Interface Selectable

All Known Subinterfaces:
Selectable.SelectionMethods
public interface Selectable

A marker interface that marks visualizations as supporting selection and the select event. It might have been nice to have some characteristic methods in the interface instead of just having the marker, but Visualization extends JavaScriptObject, and subclasses of JavaScriptObjects may not implement interfaces with methods.

Nested Class Summary
static interface Selectable.SelectionMethods
          The SelectionMethods interface can be implemented to provide the selection methods in Java classes which do not extend JavaScriptObject.
